text: Doris Martha Weber (1898 Fort Atkinson, Wisconsin – 1984, Hinckley, Ohio) was an American photographer. Her work is included in the collections of the Seattle Art Museum and the Akron Art Museum. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1984 deaths Category:People from Fort Atkinson, Wisconsin Category:Artists from Wisconsin Category:20th-century American women artists
